_team\", \"score\": 0.9964948081234408, \"rank\": 0.002721143030376833, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 515, \"end\": 521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.5614572068237247, \"rank\": 0.762161651183594, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Valieva wasrecently disqualified from the sportby Switzerland's Court of Arbitration for Sport (CAS).\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 574, \"end\": 585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.7198162141102998, \"rank\": 0.3777657227070042, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They ruled that the then 15-year-old violated anti-doping rules when she tested positive for a heart medication called\\u00a0trimetazidine, which she claimed she accidentally ingested.\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 804, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The drug has been prohibited by the World Anti-Doping Agency since 2014.\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 877, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Valieva is now 17, and the ban will lift in time for the 2026 Italy Games.\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 952, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the\\u00a0International Skating Union said since the ruling that there will be an amended scoring system from the Beijing competition.\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 989, \"end\": 994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999445208, \"